1. *Poginuo* je u ratu. (He died in the war.)
2. *Poginula* je u saobraćajnoj nesreći. (She died in a car accident.)
3. *Poginuli* su u vazdušnoj ofanzivi. (They died in an air offensive.)
4. *Poginuoše* u nesrećnom incidentu. (They perished in an unfortunate incident.)
5. *Poginuće* u borbi za slobodu. (They will die in the fight for freedom.)